00:00:25.675 --> 00:00:30.561
I'm making Coconut Sweet Lassi

00:00:36.050 --> 00:00:38.456
Ingredients required to make Coconut Sweet Lassi

00:00:38.768 --> 00:00:43.592
Curd, Sugar, Mixed Fruit Jam, Fresh Cream, Coconut Milk

00:00:53.647 --> 00:00:59.618
Take 100 gm of curd into a bowl

00:01:07.623 --> 00:01:12.801
Add 60 gm of sugar

00:01:27.319 --> 00:01:32.378
Whisk the curd and sugar till the sugar dissolves

00:01:47.544 --> 00:01:55.480
Add 30 gm of fresh cream to the curd

00:02:09.692 --> 00:02:16.141
Whisk for another 1 -2 mins

00:02:21.468 --> 00:02:29.845
Add 40 ml of coconut milk

00:02:42.581 --> 00:02:48.955
Take the lassi into a serving glass

00:02:53.052 --> 00:02:58.789
Decorate the lassi with some fruit jam

